{|{{Infobox ship begin <!-- age of sail --> |infobox caption= <!-- keywords: yes, nodab; or caption text --> |display title= <!-- keywords: none, ital; or article title with markup --> }} {{Infobox ship image |Ship image= |Ship image size= |Ship caption= }} {{Infobox ship career |Hide header= |Ship country= |Ship flag= |Ship name=*''Frem'' (1919–40) *''Vestvåg'' (1940–58) *''Vest'' (1958–68) *''Marilyn Anne'' (since 1968) |Ship owner=*Erik B Kromann (1919–39) *Janne Neilsen (1939–58) *Commune of Struer (since 1978) |Ship ordered= |Ship builder=Erik B. Kromann |Ship original cost= |Ship laid down= |Ship launched=1919 |Ship acquired= |Ship commissioned= |Ship decommissioned= |Ship in service= |Ship out of service= |Ship identification=*{{MMSI Number|219012175}} *Code Letters NWFH (1919-34) *{{ICS|November}}{{ICS|Whiskey}}{{ICS|Foxtrot}}{{ICS|Hotel}} *Code Letters OUTB (1934–39) *{{ICS|Oscar}}{{ICS|Uniform}}{{ICS|Tango}}{{ICS|Bravo}} *Code Letters SEFW (1939–40) *{{ICS|Sierra}}{{ICS|Echo}}{{ICS|Foxtrot}}{{ICS|Whiskey}} *Code Letters SFBI (1940–58) *{{ICS|Sierra}}{{ICS|Foxtrot}}{{ICS|Bravo}}{{ICS|India}} *Code Letters OWLP (1958– ) *{{ICS|Oscar}}{{ICS|Whiskey}}{{ICS|Lima}}{{ICS|Papa}} |Ship registry=*{{flagicon|Denmark}} [[Marstal]], Denmark (1919–39) *{{flagicon|Sweden}} [[Skårhamn]], Sweden (1939–58) *{{flagicon|Denmark}} [[Aalborg]], Denmark (1958–68) *{{flagicon|Denmark}} [[Struer, Denmark]] (since 1978) |Ship reinstated= |Ship honours= |Ship honors= |Ship captured= |Ship fate= |Ship status= |Ship notes= }} {{Infobox ship characteristics |Hide header= |Header caption= |Ship class= |Ship tons burthen=*{{GRT|136}}, {{NRT|119}} (1919-32) *{{GRT|141}}, {{NRT|107}} (1932- ) |Ship length={{convert|92|ft|7|in|m|2|abbr=on|order=flip}} |Ship beam={{convert|24|ft|7|in|m|2|abbr=on|order=flip}} |Ship draught={{convert|8|ft|6|in|m|2|abbr=on|order=flip}} |Ship depth={{convert|9|ft|5|in|m|2|abbr=on|order=flip}} |Ship propulsion=Sails, also auxiliary engine since 1932. |Ship sail p